      "writtenOn": "2017-01-11T17:50:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The previous way to implement this would have involved passing the struct *storage.Client directly into here.  Instead, we create an interface composed of methods from gs (the common gs implementation) and fuzzer/go/storage (for fuzzer specific gcs code).  \n\nThis is also an explicit way of specifying what RemoteDeduplicator needs to do with GCS.",
